%h1 Create a new team
%p Give the group a descriptive name, like "on-call support" or "afterhours staff", then you'll invite people to join the team who can receive notifications.
= simple_form_for @team, :html => { :class => 'form-horizontal' } do |f|
  = f.input :name, autofocus: true
  = f.button :submit, "Create team", :class => 'btn-primary'
